# urlBookmarkData

**Type Property**

A type that represents a URL bookmark.

## Declaration

```swift
static var urlBookmarkData: UTType { get }
```

## Discussion

The identifier for this type is `com.apple.bookmark`.

This type conforms to [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeData] and [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeResolvable].

## URLs

- **url**: A type that represents a URL.
- **fileURL**: A type that represents a URL to a file in the file system.
